data.description: Owner requested a drastic price drop to sell. This beautiful spacious home features 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a brick attached garage. Newer Roof, Furnace and Hot Water tank. Recently remodeled basement with a fireplace on each level. A huge yard for family gatherings and the Ultimate Basement with everything needed. Walk outside to hear the birds chirping in the mornings or take a brisk quiet walk to the Grocery store, Restaurants or shopping. It's just a hop from the 95th street corridor. Bring Clients and make an offer now as the owner is eager to relocate.
